952. J Clin Invest. 2022 Feb 15;132(4):e141848. doi: 10.1172/JCI141848.

Age-related GSK3β overexpression drives podocyte senescence and glomerular 
aging.

Fang Y(1)(2)(3), Chen B(1)(4), Liu Z(3), Gong AY(1), Gunning WT(5), Ge Y(1), 
Malhotra D(1), Gohara AF(5), Dworkin LD(1)(2)(4), Gong R(1)(2)(4)(6).

